                            },
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.invokeScript",
                                    "id": "28eae22e-f252-4711-84e2-2fd40f8a0feb",
                                    "scriptId": "feab04f2-ce06-48c8-ba47-75494084a663",
                                    "entryPointId": "",
                                    "currentScope": "Scenes",
                                    "currentSceneId": "ea6c0ba0-0d23-4c0d-80ed-b8611588a665",
                                    "currentActorId": null,
                                    "currentStoryEventId": null,
                                    "currentPropId": null
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.invokeScript",
                                    "id": "745a2e5f-6895-42c1-8bdf-269f297682b8",
                                    "scriptId": "63b3052c-fb12-4a29-b7db-17ee01dbdae1",
                                    "entryPointId": "",
                                    "currentScope": "Scenes",
                                    "currentSceneId": "ea6c0ba0-0d23-4c0d-80ed-b8611588a665",
                                    "currentActorId": null,
                                    "currentStoryEventId": null,
                                    "currentPropId": null
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "880abd01-3abd-4fb4-82a5-dc753be78f23",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Thus far, the thief continues to scavenge this school and none of you have uncovered the culprit. If this continues, the Headmaster will take Herr Terk's accusations against the Rogue Class seriously.",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "23fadcdd-72b1-4bc0-9a6c-e6c1f5571a8d",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "You must uncover the thief before you are all expelled.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "device": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "38a2bf7d-d346-494e-afa2-31f1a75b1ded",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "I admit that it is not an easy task. Clearly, the perpetrator knows this castle well. He has gotten into locked rooms with the ease of an experienced Rogue. ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "device": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.invokeScript",
                                    "id": "c1166350-db49-41cd-87a0-6033029211c2",
                                    "scriptId": "050c7bbf-88d0-4d5d-ada3-dc5f62e83860",
                                    "entryPointId": "",
                                    "currentScope": "Scenes",
                                    "currentSceneId": "ea6c0ba0-0d23-4c0d-80ed-b8611588a665",
                                    "currentActorId": null,
                                    "currentStoryEventId": null,
                                    "currentPropId": null
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "89ee485f-5d16-4420-8ab2-f512b1643f1a",
                                    "actorId": "0b49e2c8-5b7f-4534-bd10-21a0a36a6cbe",
                                    "actorId2": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "text": "How do you know that the thief isn't one of us? ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "1a2fcede-c756-4816-b8f6-e9371822e331",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": "0b49e2c8-5b7f-4534-bd10-21a0a36a6cbe",
                                    "text": "I have observed the skill with which you open the simplest of locks, Fr√§ulein MacMichael. I can reassure you that you are not a suspect in this matter.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "3",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.invokeScript",
                                    "id": "6db3b2d9-d7d4-43fc-a577-84ea938cdf9d",
                                    "scriptId": "63b3052c-fb12-4a29-b7db-17ee01dbdae1",
                                    "entryPointId": "",
                                    "currentScope": "Scenes",
                                    "currentSceneId": "ea6c0ba0-0d23-4c0d-80ed-b8611588a665",
                                    "currentActorId": null,
                                    "currentStoryEventId": null,
                                    "currentPropId": null
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "c0b0eb12-363e-4a9a-a679-4902db86bf8e",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "While several of you have the skill to open locks with ease, you also display more subtlety and cleverness than the thief. Why would anyone steal Professor Featherstonehaugh's tea set? It's not magical in and of itself. Besides, the teapot is chipped and of dubious resell value.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "device": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "733f9d73-7518-4ea7-9331-3c10d35294ef",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "The thief has stolen few things of great value and many things of little or no value. Unless one of you intended to destroy the school for Rogues, you have no motivation for the thefts.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "device": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "8b410a48-0e01-451e-830e-4d0f32384a9b",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "In addition, the thief seems to have knowledge of the secret ways and hidden passages of this castle. Therefore, I believe it is time for a lesson on 'die Versteckten sehen.' Or in the vernacular, 'Spot Hidden.'",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "device": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "63988aa7-90db-48ee-a9b1-4e8373e15b6d",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "This castle has many concealed doors and secret passageways. It takes skill to detect concealed doors. You have to look for places that do not quite make sense. Why is there no picture on a given wall? Why is there a trail in the dust leading up to a curtain?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "device": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "32048417-142e-4323-bcd3-27f31fa0b3d7",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Spot Hidden takes keen perception skills as well as the intelligence of knowing where to look. Your assignment this day is to use your skills of observation and perception to uncover the thief.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "c101d9b8-298c-4b6f-87ab-d11177a39afe",
                                    "type": "nodes.improveSkill",
                                    "skill": "Perception",
                                    "amount": "10",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "03f405e1-fd33-4747-a0f4-eb529b0f265a",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Any further questions?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "device": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                                    "id": "5d924d30-1131-4e83-855f-0b2a635cb235",
                                    "options": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "35fab00c-b5d3-4903-b38a-bab191a31446",
                                            "text": "Ask About Spot Hidden",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.invokeScript",
                                                    "id": "419daef0-6d44-4c9d-aacb-b85c3f8a0a26",
                                                    "scriptId": "a1211ed7-f6fe-4e46-8e28-e908e2f46b61",
                                                    "entryPointId": "",
                                                    "currentScope": "Scenes",
                                                    "currentSceneId": "ea6c0ba0-0d23-4c0d-80ed-b8611588a665",
                                                    "currentActorId": null,
                                                    "currentStoryEventId": null,
                                                    "currentPropId": null
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "89d716e3-7d67-4fa8-a14c-9491a8e0e4b2",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                                    "text": "So what are we supposed to look for to find hidden doors?",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "f50fac3f-d9b5-437d-a873-804ec43c5d15",
                                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "Observe the pattern of cracks on a wall. Feel whether there is a breeze moving through a room with only one main door and no windows. Listen for sounds - concealed doors are thinner than walls.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.invokeScript",
                                                    "id": "c858df6f-f9fa-4c0b-9277-68d6b51aea88",
                                                    "scriptId": "63b3052c-fb12-4a29-b7db-17ee01dbdae1",
                                                    "entryPointId": "",
                                                    "currentScope": "Scenes",
                                                    "currentSceneId": "ea6c0ba0-0d23-4c0d-80ed-b8611588a665",
                                                    "currentActorId": null,
                                                    "currentStoryEventId": null,
                                                    "currentPropId": null
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "ed84225d-a98f-4d54-b2f9-86f18267772a",
                                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                                    "actorId2": null,
                                                    "text": "Spot Hidden is not limited to just using your eyes to see what is obvious. It is using your mind to discern what is incongruous or unlikely, and discovering what someone else concealed.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": "5",
                                            "ExitMenu": true
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "047f3329-c0e2-4fd3-ba01-5cc4231b4f89",
                                            "text": "Ask About Secret Passageways",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "80b56853-e833-48be-9845-68fe9b8cde32",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                                    "text": "Couldn't you just show us an example of a secret passage around here so that we'd know better what to look for?",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "77d958fe-2837-4efb-a7ed-c6ffa2bb00fa",
                                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "I could, yes. However, this is not a kindergarten. I am not here to hold your hand as you cross the street.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "3",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "803eaca2-2465-4b4d-89e4-167304add8ba",
                                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "I am your guide, not your guardian. It is up to you to discover whether you are worthy of becoming a Rogue... or not.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "3",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.invokeScript",
                                                    "id": "19fd5771-16bf-4c8f-b35a-e542c363ceac",
                                                    "scriptId": "63b3052c-fb12-4a29-b7db-17ee01dbdae1",
                                                    "entryPointId": "",
                                                    "currentScope": "Scenes",
                                                    "currentSceneId": "ea6c0ba0-0d23-4c0d-80ed-b8611588a665",
                                                    "currentActorId": null,
                                                    "currentStoryEventId": null,
                                                    "currentPropId": null
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": "4",
                                            "ExitMenu": true
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "0806badd-02e2-4f51-a66e-c32eb9f71fac",
                                            "text": "Ask a Snarky Question",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.invokeScript",
                                                    "id": "733359e5-ed36-4154-9ba1-29302dc0dce0",
                                                    "scriptId": "a1211ed7-f6fe-4e46-8e28-e908e2f46b61",
                                                    "entryPointId": "",
                                                    "currentScope": "Scenes",
                                                    "currentSceneId": "ea6c0ba0-0d23-4c0d-80ed-b8611588a665",
                                                    "currentActorId": null,
                                                    "currentStoryEventId": null,
                                                    "currentPropId": null
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "406e5179-fb7b-4044-857e-e41d1a05da39",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                                    "text": "If it's so important that the thief is caught - why aren't you trying to catch the thief yourself? Surely you have better thief skills... er, Rogue skills... than anyone else here.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "id": "44116293-e454-4187-a883-bb0b7a342891",
                                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                                    "target": "25",
                                                    "success": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": [
                                                            {
                                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                                "id": "af56ff8c-d9ba-47b2-9a2b-e2934478ec2e",
                                                                "actorId": "4b05c425-ca25-4abb-9a36-7d793370842f",
                                                                "amount": "1",
                                                                "change": "1",
                                                                "notify": true
                                                            }
                                                        ]
                                                    },
                                                    "failure": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": [
                                                            {
                                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                                "id": "6032a933-fe2c-4b78-81f7-f1a782f93697",
                                                                "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                                                "amount": "1",
                                                                "change": "0",
                                                                "notify": true
                                                            }
                                                        ]
                                                    },
                                                    "notify": true
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "3d0fe6b1-e96e-4e28-89a7-726ac53186d1",
                                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "If this Rogue Class is disbanded because of false accusations, I shall go on with my life elsewhere. You, on the other hand, will find your future back on the streets of Sardonia far bleaker than it will be after taking this class.",
                                                    "emotion": "3",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.invokeScript",
                                                    "id": "f530ec9e-7044-43cc-aa36-0b7d5f9e85c4",
                                                    "scriptId": "63b3052c-fb12-4a29-b7db-17ee01dbdae1",
                                                    "entryPointId": "",
                                                    "currentScope": "Scenes",
                                                    "currentSceneId": "ea6c0ba0-0d23-4c0d-80ed-b8611588a665",
                                                    "currentActorId": null,
                                                    "currentStoryEventId": null,
                                                    "currentPropId": null
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "56ed91b8-f875-495a-a191-beeebacf9fca",
                                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                                    "actorId2": null,
                                                    "text": "You all are the ones who will suffer because of another's wrongdoings. It is up to you absolve yourselves of the blame and bring the thief to justice. After all, why else are you here at the university for Heroes but to become heroes?",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": "7",
                                            "ExitMenu": true
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "3c0920f8-aa37-4932-9446-f39893ab7877",
                                            "text": "Say Nothing",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.invokeScript",
                                                    "id": "4cac0131-6c1c-4c6a-85f2-4d46267e06ea",
                                                    "scriptId": "b200ef65-81a0-4f26-ab13-0f2a0f2b351e",
                                                    "entryPointId": "",
                                                    "currentScope": "Scenes",
                                                    "currentSceneId": "ea6c0ba0-0d23-4c0d-80ed-b8611588a665",
                                                    "currentActorId": null,
                                                    "currentStoryEventId": null,
                                                    "currentPropId": null
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "26a4d02c-18ec-4e05-a705-63e240955d73",
                                                    "actorId": "2ae7a408-9338-4b78-af6b-ba7a28e050ac",
                                                    "actorId2": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                                    "text": "Excellent lesson, Master von Urwald. I will use this technique to uncover the thief and restore the honor to our class.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "98d47f5a-357c-45f3-b816-d33f845c88bb",
                                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                                    "actorId2": "2ae7a408-9338-4b78-af6b-ba7a28e050ac",
                                                    "text": "Very good, Herr Sosi.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": 0,
                                            "ExitMenu": true
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                                    "Unique": false
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.invokeScript",
                                    "id": "01c26953-ab8a-4c41-ae8c-5f24e8915cf8",
                                    "scriptId": "63b3052c-fb12-4a29-b7db-17ee01dbdae1",
                                    "entryPointId": "",
                                    "currentScope": "Scenes",
                                    "currentSceneId": "ea6c0ba0-0d23-4c0d-80ed-b8611588a665",
                                    "currentActorId": null,
                                    "currentStoryEventId": null,
                                    "currentPropId": null
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "4fd452d2-b52e-42c2-bde1-83a39d7d9a0c",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Very well. I suggest that you spend your spare time uncovering the secrets of this school. More critically, I suggest you discover the thief of this school.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "device": "0"
                                },
                                {
